  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;for a project to improve public accountability and service delivery in public primary schools&quot;</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">&quot;The National Taxpayers Association (NTA) helps Kenyan citizens make the connection between the taxes they pay and the quality of the services they receive. Through this project NTA would involve parents in monitoring key aspects of schooling and then help parents and communities address areas of concern. They would also conduct background studies to understand the current tax structure at the national and county levels as well as opportunities for greater transparency, accountability, and pro-poor targeting of government revenue. Through broadly sharing findings from each of these projects NTA hopes to strengthen community voice in demanding accountability and quality service provision across Kenya.&quot;</narrative>
  </description>
